text.tspan: Annual change in female population under the age of 25, 1951 to 2100
Population yearly increment, estimated as the difference between the population on 1st of July of the year
indicated and the population a year before. This only includes females aged 0-24. Projections from 2024
onwards are based on the UN's high scenario.
Data source: UN, World Population Prospects (2024)
